0said%20they're%20glad%20that%20the%20tariffs%20were%20lowered%2C%20but%20that%2090%20days%20is%20not%20long%20enough%20to%20make%20decisions%20confidently%20%E2%80%94%20now%2C%20business%20feels%20like%20a%20guessing%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2283008fd9-982f-4e94-8b88-95a7050e7194%5C%22%3ERacing%20against%20the%20clock%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20tariffs%20were%20at%20145%25%2C%20Alexander%20said%20he'd%20paused%20production%20on%20two%20projects%20for%20his%20company%20Coyote%20and%20Crow%20Games%2C%20which%20produces%20board%20and%20card%20games%20that%20represent%20the%20Indigenous%20community.%20He%20decided%20to%20green%20light%20both%20games%20when%20the%20trade%20deal%20went%20into%20effect%2C%20partly%20because%20he'd%20already%20sunk%20years%20and%20money%20into%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Alexander%20isn't%20sure%20that%20he'll%20be%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20new%20rates%2C%20which%20are%20significantly%20higher%20than%20before%20the%20trade%20war%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20fastest%20circumstances%2C%2090%20days%20may%20not%20be%20long%20enough%20to%20get%20his%20game%20that's%20currently%20being%20printed%20in%20China%20to%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20with%20potential%20shipping%20delays.%20He%20has%20no%20idea%20what%20taxes%20he'll%20end%20up%20paying%20on%20the%20game%20when%20it%20arrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaley%20Pavone%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Pashion%20Footwear%2C%20which%20makes%20convertible%20heels%2C%20called%20the%20trade%20deal%20%26quot%3Ba%20mix%20of%20relief%2C%20but%20also%20frustration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20make%20a%20shoe%20in%2010%20minutes%2C%20I'd%20be%20stockpiling%20right%20now%2C%20but%20they%20take%20four%20months%20to%20make%20and%20this%20is%20only%20a%2090%20day%20reprieve%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavone%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20enough%20time%20to%20make%20any%20kind%20of%20change%20other%20than%20continuing%20to%20play%20it%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20summer%20shoes%20have%20arrived%20and%20fall%20products%20are%20in%20production%2C%20but%20she%20said%20she%20hasn't%20placed%20her%20holiday%20order%20yet.%20Pavone%20said%20that%20her%20fall%20shoes%20should%20arrive%20in%20August%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20know%20what%20taxes%20she'll%20pay%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20anyone's%20guess%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHugo%20Ramirez%2C%2042%2C%20told%20BI%20he%20typically%20buys%20all%20of%20his%20nonperishables%20from%20China%20for%20Frio%20Mexican%20Treats%2C%20an%20ice%20cream%20and%20churro%20shop%20in%20Appleton%2C%20Wisconsin%20that%20features%20flavors%20from%20his%20hometown%20of%20Chihuahua%2C%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20145%25%20tariffs%20were%20in%20effect%20he%20paused%20all%20of%20his%20orders%20from%20China%20and%20started%20buying%20from%20US%20manufacturers%20instead%2C%20but%20the%20materials%20were%20more%20expensive%20and%20not%20customized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Jessica%20Kim%2C%20the%2034-year-old%20owner%20of%20Mycha%20LA%20and%20Chicago%2C%20a%20company%20that%20operates%20vending%20machines%20for%20boba%20and%20specialty%20teas%2C%20the%2090-day%20window%20offered%20a%20brief%20opportunity%20to%20receive%20a%20shipment%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20no%20chance%20for%20long-term%20planning.%20She%20sources%20all%20of%20her%20vending%20machines%2C%20non-perishables%2C%20and%20a%20few%20specialty%20tea%20leaves%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessica%20Kim%20and%20Mycha%20tea%20team%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682764d968a2929008018d71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessica%20Kim%2C%20left%2C%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Mycha%20Chicago%20team%20buy%20their%20vending%20machines%20from%20China.%3Cp%3EJessica%20Kim%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20order%20of%2010%20machines%20that%20was%20meant%20to%20arrive%20in%20February%20was%20delayed%20and%20was%20only%20ready%20to%20be%20shipped%20at%20the%20end%20of%20April.%20Kim%20paused%20the%20order%2C%20though%2C%20because%20of%20the%20145%25%20tariffs%20in%20place%20at%20the%20time.%20When%20the%20taxes%20dropped%20to%2030%25%2C%20she%20approved%20the%20delivery%2C%20and%20the%20machines%20are%20scheduled%20to%20arrive%20by%20mid-June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20trying%20to%20time%20it%2C%20almost%20like%20gambling%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef949db5-67e3-4896-979e-5163c255daca%5C%22%3E'Guessing%20game'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAlexander%20told%20BI%20he's%20anticipating%20a%20%2410%20to%20%2420%20price%20hike%20on%20his%20games%20if%20tariffs%20stay%20at%2030%25%2C%20but%20he%20can't%20accurately%20predict%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20already%20had%20to%20tell%20my%20customer%20base%2C%20'I%20don't%20know%20what%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20to%20charge%20you%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20I'll%20know%20when%20that%20inventory%20gets%20here%2C'%26quot%3B%20Alexander%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20taking%20a%20chance.%20I'm%20gambling%20on%20my%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPavone%20said%20she%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20remain%20%26quot%3Bas%20cautious%20and%20risk-averse%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20will%20likely%20impact%20her%20supply%20and%20pricing%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we're%20trying%20to%20put%20that%20budget%20together%2C%20we're%20having%20to%20play%20a%20guessing%20game%20of%20what%20happens%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%2090%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20about%20her%20holiday%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPavone%20has%20also%20been%20impacted%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20closing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fde-min