ughput%20and%20other%20experience%20issues%20they%20need%20to%20fix%20is%20going%20to%20require%20more%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20R.J.%20Hottovy%2C%20the%20head%20of%20analytical%20research%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPlacer.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlacer.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20staffs%20up%20stores%2C%20Starbucks%20is%20also%20rolling%20out%20a%20new%20algorithm%20that%20will%20determine%20the%20order%20in%20which%20baristas%20make%20drinks.%20That%20will%20help%20baristas%20make%20drinks%20more%20efficiently%20with%20those%20extra%20shifts%2C%20the%20company%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20September%2C%20the%20new%20labor%20model%20and%20the%20algorithm%20will%20be%20in%20about%203%2C000%20US%20stores%2C%20Niccol%20said%20on%20last%20month's%20earnings%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20provides%20a%20counter-example%20to%20a%20broader%20restaurant%20industry%20trend.%20While%20many%20other%20chains%20are%20automating%20processes%2C%20especially%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwendys-expanding-ai-ordering-hundreds-more-drive-thrus-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Seattle-based%20company%20is%20acknowledging%20that%20there%20might%20be%20limits%20to%20what%20machines%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdfa491a-7b36-4fcc-804e-4f5964ead090%5C%22%3EAt%20Starbucks%2C%20machines%20haven't%20been%20as%20effective%20as%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Starbucks%20rolled%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-workers-weigh-in-on-new-machines-for-cold-brew-and-other-iced-drinks-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESiren%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20made%20a%20series%20of%20equipment%20and%20process%20improvements%20meant%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20production%20of%20cold%20beverages%20like%20frappuccinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C