3f9d464%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Peak%20Pro%20is%20manufactured%20in%20China.%3Cp%3EKathleen%20Elkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20January%202025%2C%20I%20ordered%20500%20pickleball%20paddles%20from%20a%20Chinese%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20narrowly%20avoided%20tariffs%2C%20which%20peaked%20at%20145%25%20for%20some%20Chinese%20goods.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20prepared%20to%20make%20a%20key%20strategic%20shift%3A%20transitioning%20to%20a%20supplier%20outside%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20January%202025%2C%20after%20months%20of%20prototyping%20and%20development%2C%20I%20ordered%20500%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilding-an-ecommerce-business-how-to-select-a-profitable-product-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epickleball%20paddles%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20a%20Chinese%20manufacturer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESix%20weeks%20and%20one%20long%20boat%20ride%20later%2C%20five%20weathered%20boxes%20of%2050%20each%20arrived%20at%20my%20doorstep%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20shipped%20directly%20to%20Amazon%20warehouses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inventory%20cost%20my%20business%20partner%20and%20me%20a%20little%20over%20%2411%2C000.%20Had%20we%20ordered%20the%20product%20a%20little%20later%2C%20when%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20tariffs%20on%20all%20imports%20from%20China%20to%20the%20US%2C%20our%20bill%20could%20have%20been%20much%20steeper.%20Tariffs%20on%20China%20started%20at%2010%25%20in%20February%2C%20peaked%20at%20145%25%20in%20April%2C%20and%20were%2030%25%20as%20of%20May%2012.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20good%20timing%20for%20us.%20We'd%20already%20dealt%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lanch-ecommerce-company-startup-costs-expenses-business-budget-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunexpected%20costs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20launching%20our%20brand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.peakpickleballco.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeak%20Pickleball%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20tariffs%20would%20have%20sent%20us%20even%20further%20over%20budget.%20While%20we%20shouldn't%20need%20to%20order%20more%20inventory%20anytime%20soon%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20but%20wonder%2C%20as%20a%20novice%20in%20the%20e-commerce%20space%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshould%20I%20be%20worried%20about%20working%20exclusively%20with%20suppliers%20in%20China%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20called%20up%20Tyler%20Walter%2C%20who%20co-founded%20a%20supply%20chain%20services%20company%20for%20brands%20in%20the%20US%20in%202021.%20The%20mission%20of%20the%20company%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.330trading.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E330%20Trading%20Co.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20is%20to%20help%20smaller%2C%20US-based%20e-commerce%20companies%20diversify%20their%20supply%20chains.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20they%20help%20connect%20business%20owners%20like%20me%20with%20manufacturers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they%20specialize%20in%20moving%20companies%20beyond%20China%20to%20suppliers%20in%20Taiwan%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20other%20regions%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYears%20ago%2C%20the%20330%20Trading%20co-founders%20noticed%20a%20trend%20%E2%80%94%20big%20brands%20like%20Nike%2C%20Adidas%2C%20and%20Lululemon%20were%20transitioning%20away%20from%20Chinese%20suppliers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20help%20smaller%20brands%20that%20didn't%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20connect%20with%20factories%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BChina%20is%20really%20good%20at%20marketing%20their%20factories%20and%20managing%20relationships%20with%20outside%20companies.%20They've%20been%20doing%20it%20for%2040%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Walter%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20Taipei%20and%20is%20on%20the%20ground%20building%20relationships%20with%20factories%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20told%20me%20back%20in%202023.%20However%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20factories%20in%20places%20like%20Vietnam%20or%20Thailand%20or%20Malaysia%20that%20can%20make%20those%20baseball%20caps%20or%20those%20hoodies%20that%20you%20want%20to%20sell.%20They%20just%20don't%20have%20any%20way%20of%20finding%20customers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20and%20the%20US%20brand%20owners%20have%20no%20way%20of%20finding%20those%20factories%20because%20of%20cultural%20and%20language%20barriers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20more%20so%20than%20ever%2C%20it's%20important%20for%20businesses%20to%20have%20diverse%20supply%20chains%2C%20which%20is%20why%20my%20business%20partner%20and%20I%20are%20prepared%20to%20make%20a%20key%20strategic%20shift%3A%20transitioning%20to%20a%20supplier%20outside%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225e951e1e-e930-4c85-be0e-880c175d1daa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20mitigate%20tariffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20hundreds%20of%20pickleball%20paddles%20still%20to%20sell%2C%20I%20won't%20be%20placing%20a%20second%20inventory%20order%20anytime%20soon.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20a%20misprint%20on%20our%20first%20round%20of%20inventory%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20agreed%20to%20send%20us%20250%20complimentary%20paddles.%20Those%20are%20still%20in%20China.%20And%20while%20we%20don't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20paddles%2C%20we%20would%20still%20pay%20tariffs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWalter%20recommended%20we%20hold%20that%20shipment%2C%20anticipating%20that%20tariffs%20would%20eventually%20drop.%20Four%20days%20after%20our%20conversation%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20said%20it%20would%20reduce%20the%20145%25%20tariff%20to%2030%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20our%20second%20order%2C%20assuming%20we%20work%20through%20our%20initial%20inventory%20and%20tariffs%20are%20still%20in%20effect%2C%20I%20asked%20him%20to%20explain%20what%20that%20would%20look%20like%20and%20mean%20for%20our%20business.%20%3Cem%3EHow%20much%20would%20tariffs%20actually%20cost%2C%20and%20is%20there%20anything%20we%20can%20do%20to%20mitigate%20them%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20told%20me%20that%2C%20first%2C%20it's%20key%20to%20understand%20exactly%20what%20we're%20being%20taxed%20on%3A%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20product%2C%20not%20the%20sales%20price.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22peak%20pickleball%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67479279ede4eeae392a2a00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20first%20shipment%20of%20Peak%20Pro%20paddles%20arrived%20in%20early%202025%20and%20avoided%20tariffs.%20%3Cp%3EKatie%20Monds%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSay%20you%20bought%20these%20paddles%20for%20%2420%20and%20then%20you're%20selling%20them%20for%20%2460.%20Some%20really%20novice%20rookies%20will%20actually%20get%20taxed%20on%20that%20%2460%20because%20they%20don't%20know%20that's%20how%20it%20works%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20getting%20taxed%20145%25%20based%20on%20the%20%2420%20value%2C%20not%20the%20%2460%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20said%20we%20could%20likely%20get%20taxed%20on%20even%20less%20than%20the%20%2420%20value%20because%20included%20in%20that%20cost%20is%20the%20profit%20that%20the%20suppliers%20of%20each%20of%20the%20paddle's%20components%20(the%20carbon%20fiber%2C%20the%20plastic%2C%20the%20wrap%20that%20goes%20around%20the%20handle%2C%20etc.)%20took%20home%2C%20meaning%20the%20product%20itself%20is%20valued%20at%20less%20than%20%2420.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it%20might%20end%20up%20being%20%2415%20or%20even%20%2410%20on%20the%20official%20invoice%20when%20the%20products%20come%20into%20the%20country%2C%20and%20then%20you're%20taxed%20based%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Walter%2C%20which%20can%20make%20a%20big%20difference.%20Assuming%20a%20145%25%20tariff%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20put%20%2460%20on%20the%20invoice%2C%20you%20would%20pay%20a%20%2490%20tariff%20per%20paddle%3B%20if%20you%20put%20%2420%20on%20the%20invoice%2C%20you%20would%20pay%20a%20%2430%20tariff%20per%20paddle%3B%20but%20if%20you%20put%20%2410%2C%20you%20would%20pay%20a%20%2415%20tariff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20I%20understand%20exactly%20how%20much%20I'd%20owe%20per%20paddle%2C%20I%20can%20decide%20how%20to%20move%20forward%2C%20my%20two%20main%20options%20being%3A%20eat%20the%20tariff%20or%20find%20a%20different%20manufacturer%20in%20a%20different%20country%20with%20lower%20tariffs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20of%20Walter's%20customers%20are%20choosing%20to%20eat%20the%20cost%20because%20they%20can%20afford%20it%2C%20and%20it%20outweighs%20the%20expense%20of%20going%20out%20of%20stock%20or%20moving%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20products%20where%20they%20might%20be%20paying%20%245%20for%20it%20out%20of%20China%2C%20and%20they%20sell%20it%20for%20%2450%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20types%20of%20businesses%20exist%2C%20and%20if%20they%20have%20to%20pay%20an%20extra%20%245%20in%20tariffs%20per%20item%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20break%20their%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20for%20small%20businesses%20with%20smaller%20profit%20margins%2C%20it's%20not%20that%20simple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20option%2C%20transitioning%20manufacturers%2C%20is%20also%20not%20that%20simple.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EE-commerce%20entrepreneur%20Shan%20Shan%20Fu%20told%20me%20that%20switching%20suppliers%20isn't%20feasible.%20She%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-amazon-entrepreneurship-ecommerce-business-side-hustle-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esells%20over%20100%20products%20on%20Amazon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20women's%20clothing%20and%20accessory%20space.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20100%20products%20come%20from%20all%20different%20factories%2C%20so%20to%20change%20and%20have%20another%20factory%20in%2C%20say%20Vietnam%2C%20replicate%20what%20many%2C%20many%20factories%20are%20already%20making%2C%20and%20making%20it%20at%20the%20same%20quality%20and%20level%2C%20is%20going%20to%20take%20years%20and%20years%20and%20years%2C%20and%20it%20would%20cost%20more%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22shan%20shan%20fu%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F636adc93113fe10018351eaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShan%20Shan%20Fu%20sells%20about%20100%20products%20on%20Amazon%2C%20including%20socks%20and%20tights.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Shan%20Shan%20Fu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20factories%20require%20a%20minimum%20order%20quantity%2C%20she%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BSo%20they'll%20say%2C%20'We%20can't%20custom-make%20anything%20for%20you%20unless%20you%20order%202%2C000%20pieces.'%20But%20if%20you're%20a%20small%20business%2C%20often%20you%20can't%20buy%202%2C000%20pieces%20right%20away%3B%20you%20might%20buy%20200%2C%20then%20500%2C%20then%201%2C000%2C%20and%20you%20scale%20up%20slowly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20most%20small%20businesses%2C%20suddenly%20having%20to%20place%20a%20large%20order%20with%20new%20suppliers%20%26quot%3Bjust%20isn't%20doable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20flexibility%20to%20leave%20China.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFu%20says%20she's%20in%20a%20holding%20pattern%2C%20waiting%20and%20hoping%20for%20tariffs%20to%20lower%20or%2C%20ideally%2C%20disappear.%20She%20doesn't%20want%20to%20wait%20too%20long%2C%20though%2C%20or%20else%20she'll%20have%20empty%20shelves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22316714a9-ab4c-4a13-ad19-3388ffc7cb8b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransitioning%20away%20from%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnlike%20Fu%2C%20I%20have%20a%20single%20product%2C%20which%20should%20make%20switching%20manufacturers%20less%20complex.%20Walter%20said%20my%20business%20partner%20and%20I%20should%20consider%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20assured%20us%20that%20we%20shouldn't%20have%20done%20anything%20differently%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20generally%20much%20cheaper%20and%20faster%20to%20get%20a%20product%20off%20the%20ground%20with%20a%20Chinese%20supplier.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BChina%20just%20makes%20a%20lot%20more%20sense%20for%20the%20development%20of%20a%20product.%20Their%20efficiency%20is%20unrivaled.%20They're%20so%20fast%20at%20turning%20around%20the%20development%20samples%20and%20opening%20molds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20But%2C%20%26quot%3Bonce%20you%20guys%20have%20sales%20and%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20appetite%20for%20risk%20and%20money%20to%20spend%2C%20then%20we%20can%20we%20can%20reevaluate%20where%20you%20might%20want%20to%20do%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20we%20sell%20our%20first%20couple%20of%20hundred%20paddles%2C%20it%20may%20be%20time%20to%20consider%20a%20different%20supplier%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20likely%20won't%20be%20the%20only%20ones%20looking%20to%20transition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20this%2090-day%20pause%20that%20we're%20currently%20in%2C%20I%20think%20that%20regardless%20of%20where%20we're%20at%2C%20Southeast%20Asia%20is%20still%20going%20to%20be%20way%20more%20attractive%20than%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Walter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-mitigate-trump-tariffs-ecommerce-business-diversify-supply-chain-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747479721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682792143fe8d39283661f24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-mitigate-trump-tariffs-ecommerce-business-diversify-supply-chain-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I've%20avoided%20tariffs%20so%20far%20but%20couldn't%20help%20but%20wonder%2C%20should%20I%20be%20worried%20about%20working%20exclusively%20with%20suppliers%20in%20China%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-mitigate-trump-tariffs-ecommerce-business-diversify-supply-chain-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pedro%20Pascal%20Says%20%E2%80%98F%E2%80%94%20the%20People%20That%20Try%20to%20Make%20You%20Scared%E2%80%99%20When%20Asked%20About%20U.S.%20Political%20Chaos%3A%20%E2%80%98Fight%20Back.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Let%20Them%20Win%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747479660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fpedro-2.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236401603%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pedro%20Pascal%20had%20a%20strong%20message%20about%20the%20current%20political%20chaos%20in%20the%20U.S.%20at%20the%20Cannes%20press%20conference%20for%20%E2%80%9CEddington%2C%E2%80%9D%20telling%20journalists%3A%20%E2%80%9CFuck%20the%20people%20who%20t