2C%20but%20also%20one%20of%20the%20more%20confusing%20ones.%20Twelve%20winners%20will%20get%20to%20make%20ramen%20with%20the%20rapper%2C%20dress%20up%20in%20a%20costume%2C%20and%20play%20Xbox%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20description%20of%20the%20actual%20run%20of%20events%20looks%20like%20this%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22591%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mega%20thee%20stallion's%20aribnb%20desription%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68260993c6ad288d1481083b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22305%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20event%20includes%20getting%20a%20costume%2C%20a%20video%20game%2C%20and%20finally%20meeting%20Megan%20for%20a%20shot%20of%20tequila.%3Cp%3EAirbnb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20slightly%20less%20famous%20celebrity%20experiences%20that%20do%20charge.%20Brooklyn%20Peltz%20Beckham%20(son%20of%20David%20and%20Victoria%2C%20son-in-law%20of%20billionaire%20businessman%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-proxy-war-nelson-peltz-conslation-prize-bob-iger-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENelson%20Peltz%3C%2Fa%3E)%20offers%20a%20cooking%20demonstration%20for%20%24150%20per%20guest.%20Pro%20wrestlers%20Nikki%20and%20Brie%20Garcia%20offer%20a%20chance%20to%20sit%20in%20on%20their%20podcast%20taping%20for%20%24195.%20Chance%20the%20Rapper%20is%20having%20a%20listening%20party%20for%20%24110.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20rep%20for%20Airbnb%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20pricing%20was%20up%20to%20the%20celebrity%20and%20that%20another%20A-list%20celebrity%20would%20soon%20be%20doing%20a%20paid%20event%2C%20with%20the%20fees%20going%20to%20charity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c8a4999-70e6-4f20-9438-484c7af5de65%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20actually%20win%20these%20free%20experiences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20disconnect%20here%20between%20these%20star-studded%20promotional%20things%20and%20the%20new%20Experiences%20Airbnb%20is%20trying%20to%20promote.%20These%20are%20largely%20contests%20to%20win%20a%20free%20prize%2C%20not%20an%20experience%20or%20service%20you%20pay%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20unlike%20a%20classic%20radio%20station%20contest%20where%20the%2025th%20caller%20gets%20to%20meet%20Paul%20Stanley%2C%20or%20the%201990s%20MTV%20contests%20where%20suburban%20teens%20can%20win%20the%20chance%20for%20a%20big%20band%20to%20perform%20in%20their%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FR4sgH0x1Ors%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22White%20Zombie%20MTV%20Invades%20Your%20Space%20Contest%20Winner%20Back%20Yard%20Performance%2010-21-1995%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20product%20Airbnb%20is%20launching%20is%20more%20practical%20and%20down-to-earth%3A%20high-quality%20tours%20and%20food%20experiences%20from%20vetted%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20charging%20a%20nominal%20amount%20makes%20these%20celebrity%20experiences%20very%20different.%20Airbnb%20subsidizes%20the%20event%2C%20likely%20cutting%20the%20celebrity%20a%20big%20check%20to%20participate.%20This%20is%20a%20different%20business%20model%20from%20the%20regular%20tour%20guides%2C%20who%20make%20their%20money%20from%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b7d0bff8-8d01-43e4-a837-e4168dc06265%5C%22%3EA%20prompt%20to%20fill%20out%20your%20user%20bio%20with%20more%20information%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20there%20%3Cem%3Eis%3C%2Fem%3E%20something%20that%20makes%20sense%20about%20all%20of%20this.%20I%20figured%20it%20out%20when%20I%20started%20the%20process%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20Megan%20Thee%20Stallion's%20event%20on%20the%20Airbnb%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20about%20getting%20your%20sweet%2C%20sweet%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20my%20application%20process%2C%20I%20was%20asked%20to%20continue%20to%20fill%20out%20my%20user%20bio%20%E2%80%94%20adding%20things%20like%20my%20favorite%20song%20from%20high%20school%2C%20my%20hobbies%2C%20where%20I%20went%20to%20school%2C%20and%20my%20pet's%20name%20(as%20a%20tech%20journalist%2C%20I%20must%20warn%20you%20here%20%3Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20put%20information%20in%20a%20public%20bio%20that%20is%20commonly%20used%20for%20password%20reminder%20questions).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20want%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20Patrick%20Mahomes%20and%20Megan%20Thee%20Stallion.%20Only%20a%20handful%20will%20get%20to%2C%20but%20many%20will%20fill%20out%20their%20expanded%20bios%2C%20giving%20Airbnb%20lots%20of%20information%20on%20prospective%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22airbnb%20bio%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682658c568a29290080179f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222162%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20new%2C%20expanded%20bio%20on%20Airbnb%20(I%20didn't%20fill%20out%20all%20the%20questions).%3Cp%3EAirbnb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20expanded%20bios%20are%20part%20of%20Airbnb's%20new%20ambitious%20rebrand%3A%20to%20be%20a%20place%20not%20just%20for%20vacation%20rentals%2C%20but%20for%20people%20to%20hire%20other%20people%20for%20anything.%20And%20part%20of%20that%20is%20building%20out%20is%20convincing%20customers%20to%20make%20personalized%20bios%2C%20so%20that%20the%20vendors%20can%20better%20see%20who%20they're%20dealing%20with%20and%20vice%20versa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20new%20feature%20called%20Services%20actually%20seems%20like%20a%20great%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20things%20like%20a%20hair%20stylist%20or%20makeup%20artist%20to%20come%20to%20your%20home%20or%20Airbnb%20rental